snippet.title: Hello Kitty Lunchbox | Google Play Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the app on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.budgestudios.HelloKittyLunchBox

Join Hello Kitty in the school cafeteria to choose what
scrumptious lunch to prepare. 

If you make your recipe just the way Hello Kitty wants, she’ll give you supercute rewards to decorate your lunchbox and make it extra
special!

Follow us on Facebook! www.facebook.com/budgestudios
